						   <p> Fortune Foundation for Special needs ( FFSN), was born in Dec 2018, with a vision to make a difference in the lives of children with disabilities and their families.FFSN is a registered trust formed by parents having children with autism and professionals working in the same field for years .</p>

   <p>FFSN primarily works with Autism individuals and is open to other developmental disabilities. As of now we work with children from 7 to 16 years of age.</p>

   <p>At FFSN, we provide education and quality interventions with the objective to bring the holistic development in the individual. Also being a lifelong condition, our aim is to develop appropriate pre- vocational and social skills of children so that they gainfully occupy themselves. FFSN plan in coming years is to set up a Pre- vocational center to make our children ready for work and employment in the sheltered workplace and open employment as well depending on level of support the individual needs.</p>



